sequenceDiagram
    participant Frag as NoticiasFragment
    participant Fetcher as NoticiasFetcher
    participant RSS as RTP Feed (XML)

    Frag->>Fetcher: fetchNews()
    activate Fetcher
    Fetcher->>RSS: HTTP GET
    activate RSS
    RSS-->>Fetcher: XML Response
    deactivate RSS
    Fetcher->>Fetcher: parseXML()
    Fetcher->>Fetcher: extractImages(Regex)
    Fetcher-->>Frag: List<Noticia>
    deactivate Fetcher
    Frag->>Frag: updateRecyclerView()
